#: ../../index.rst:53 dd7875a5deec45a0af1a5d7831b0c4c8
msgid "🌟 Key Features"
msgstr "🌟 核心特性"

#: ../../index.rst:55 39dec447833e42b9be9e71bfb979941c
msgid ""
"🌍 **30-Language Multilingual** - Input text directly in any of the 30 "
"supported languages in most cases, with no explicit language tag "
"required."
msgstr ""
"🌍 **30 语种多语言生成** - 支持 30 种语言，绝大多数情况下直接输入目标语言文本即可，无需额外标注语言。"

#: ../../index.rst:56 34366d2cf4cf48cd81f4affc1b669a10
msgid ""
"🎨 **Voice Design** - Create a brand-new voice from a natural-language "
"description alone, with no reference audio required."
msgstr ""
"🎨 **声音设计** - 无需参考音频，只靠自然语言描述就能创建一把全新的声音。"

#: ../../index.rst:57 8d18bfe053b34432ae1aecde85c14bd8
msgid ""
"🎛️ **Controllable Cloning** - Clone a voice from a short reference clip, "
"then steer emotion, pace, and style while preserving the original timbre."
msgstr ""
"🎛️ **可控声音克隆** - 用一段简短的参考音频克隆音色，同时还能继续调节情绪、语速与风格，并尽量保留原始音色特征。"

#: ../../index.rst:58 070d0f592a2d4e5dbf20946944fcde3d
msgid ""
"🎙️ **Ultimate Cloning** - For maximum fidelity, provide both the "
"reference audio and its transcript so the model can continue seamlessly "
"from the prompt and preserve more vocal detail."
msgstr ""
"🎙️ **高保真克隆** - 若同时提供参考音频及对应转写，模型就能更自然地承接参考语音，在音色、节奏、情绪与风格上保留更多细节。"

#: ../../index.rst:59 8204d2ca371c4a8e928f481732854f3b
msgid ""
"🔊 **48kHz High-Quality Audio** - Accepts 16kHz reference audio and "
"outputs 48kHz audio through AudioVAE V2's asymmetric encode/decode "
"design, with built-in super-resolution and no external upsampler "
"required."
msgstr ""
"🔊 **48kHz 高品质音频** - 支持输入 16kHz 参考音频，并通过 AudioVAE V2 的非对称编解码直接输出 48kHz 高品质音频，内置超分能力，无需额外上采样器。"

#: ../../index.rst:60 5285a07acb8b49feb81b40ac9bdc9311
msgid ""
"🧠 **Context-Aware Synthesis** - Automatically infers appropriate prosody "
"and expressiveness from the text itself for more natural, content-matched"
" delivery."
msgstr ""
"🧠 **理解语境的语音生成** - 能根据文本内容自动推断更合适的韵律与表达，让生成结果更自然，也更贴合语境。"

#: ../../index.rst:61 f31e94fed40d4d068b10dbd3ff30f373
msgid ""
"⚡ **Real-Time Streaming** - Reaches an RTF as low as **0.13** on NVIDIA "
"RTX 4090 with `NanoVLLM-VoxCPM <https://github.com/a710128/nanovllm-"
"voxcpm>`_ for high-throughput serving."
msgstr ""
"⚡ **实时流式生成** - 搭配 `NanoVLLM-VoxCPM <https://github.com/a710128/nanovllm-voxcpm>`_，可在 NVIDIA RTX 4090 上实现低至 **0.13** 的实时系数（RTF），适合实时场景。"

#: ../../index.rst:62 0dcbab2c4f284a2c82809280212ecdc9
msgid ""
"📦 **Fully Open-Source & Commercial-Ready** - Weights and code are "
"released under the `Apache License 2.0 "
"<https://www.apache.org/licenses/LICENSE-2.0>`_, allowing commercial use."
msgstr ""
"📦 **完全开源，可用于商业场景** - 权重与代码均以 `Apache License 2.0 <https://www.apache.org/licenses/LICENSE-2.0>`_ 发布，可用于商业用途。"

